&lt;X&gt; and &lt;Y&gt; are the screen location.<br>
&lt;COUNT&gt; is how many lines from 1 to 10<br>
&lt;FONTSIZE&gt; is a font size of 0, 1, or 2.<br>
&lt;HEADER&gt; is 1 or 0 to turn on or off the header.<br>
&lt;BG&gt; is 1 or 0 to turn on or off the background poly.<br>
&lt;WIDTH&gt; is the width of the background poly.<br>
note: m5 is only valid for My Attacks. It's ignored for other types and m<br>
<br>
my=my attacks<br>
me= me getting hit<br>
other= others attacks<br>
<br>
on= attacks are shown old fasion way, in chat box<br>
